OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FOn Tuesday Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,7,Fwill deliver her spring statement to
OL,8,Fparliament, where she'll update MPs on
OL,9,Fthe economy.
OL,11,FLast year's spring statement was a key
OL,12,Fmoment for Reeves as she tightened
OL,13,Fspending plans and announced a series
OL,14,Fof major welfare cuts.
OL,16,FBut this time around it's expected to
OL,17,Fbe much less eventful - with the
OL,18,FTreasury insisting there will be no
OL,19,Fannouncements or changes to tax or
OL,20,Fspending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
