OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FWhat is the spring statement?
OL,8,FThere are two major fiscal events for
OL,9,Fthe government each year - the Budget
OL,10,Fand the spring statement.
OL,12,FAt the Budget ministers lay out their
OL,13,Fmain plans for tax and spending, while
OL,14,Fthe spring statement is more of a mid-
OL,15,Fyear update where the government are
OL,16,Fable to make some changes.
OL,18,FBut the spring statement on Tuesday is
OL,19,Fset to be a relatively low-key affair,
OL,20,Fwith no policy announcements.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FThere will be key economic statistics
OL,7,Ffrom the Office for Budget
OL,8,FResponsibility published alongside the
OL,9,Fstatement, with projections released
OL,10,Ffor growth, inflation, unemployment,
OL,11,Fgovernment spending and tax revenues
OL,12,Fover the coming years.
OL,14,FThe government will be publishing the
OL,15,FOBR forecast itself this year after
OL,16,Fthe watchdog accidentally published
OL,17,Fthe Autumn Budget early.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
