FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FAt the Budget the OBR said the
OL,7,Fchancellor had a #21.7bn financial
OL,8,Fsafety cushion, known as "headroom" -
OL,9,Fand it's expected that won't have
OL,10,Fchanged massively.
OL,12,FWhy is this spring statement different?
OL,14,FReeves decided when she became
OL,15,Fchancellor that she would only have
OL,16,Fone fiscal event a year, with the
OL,17,FBudget being the big moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
