OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FLast year's spring statement was more
OL,7,Fof an event because it was Reeves'
OL,8,Ffirst one, where she faced a difficult
OL,9,Feconomic climate, hadn't left herself
OL,10,Fenough headroom, and announced
OL,11,Fsweeping benefits cuts which she later
OL,12,Fu-turned on.
OL,14,FThe Treasury is downplaying Tuesday's
OL,15,Fevent as far more muted, the
OL,16,Fchancellor's speech will be much
OL,17,Fshorter, and she's not expected to pop
OL,18,Fup in interviews on TV screens
OL,19,Fafterwards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
