PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FThe OBR report this year is however
OL,7,Fexpected to reflect several
OL,8,Fsignificant policy changes made since
OL,9,Fthe Budget, such as last week's #3.5
OL,10,Fbillion special educational needs
OL,11,Fspending package, the reversal of
OL,12,Fplans to introduce inheritance tax on
OL,13,Ffarmers before Christmas, and a
OL,14,Freversal earlier this year on raising
OL,15,Fbusiness rates for pubs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
