PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FThis year there will also be no
OL,7,Fassessment from the OBR on whether
OL,8,FReeves has met her self-imposed fiscal
OL,9,Frules, which say that debt should be
OL,10,Ffalling as a share of national income
OL,11,Fby 2030, and the government shouldn't
OL,12,Fborrow to fund day-to-day spending.
OL,14,FHow is the economy doing?
OL,16,FThe Labour government has made
OL,17,Feconomic growth one of their key
OL,18,Fmissions, but the growth they've so
OL,19,Ffar been able to achieve has been
OL,20,Fpretty sluggish.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
