PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772547084
OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FIt's also likely that any narrow
OL,7,Fimprovements to the economy will now
OL,8,Fbe overturned by the US-Israel war on
OL,9,FIran which has led to a spike in oil
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FAs ITV's Political Editor Robert
OL,13,FPeston observed on Monday, the war
OL,14,Fmeans "global and UK inflation will
OL,15,Falmost certainly be higher than
OL,16,Fotherwise and growth lower", and hopes
OL,17,Fof a sustained fall in energy prices
OL,18,Fis also "probably gone".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
