OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FGDP figures released in February
OL,7,Fshowed the economy grew by only 0.1%
OL,8,Fin the last three months of 2025,
OL,9,Fwhich was less than expected.
OL,11,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,12,Falso published data last month showing
OL,13,Fa higher than expected surplus from
OL,14,Ftax receipts.
OL,16,FIt was the biggest ever Budget surplus
OL,17,Fof #30.4bn recorded after an increase
OL,18,Fin self-assessment and capital gains
OL,19,Ftax receipts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
