OL,3,CWhat is the spring statement and why
OL,4,Cis this one different?
OL,6,FRetail sales improved in December,
OL,7,Fwhile interest rates were cut and
OL,8,Finflation has been falling.
OL,10,FThe energy regulator Ofgem also
OL,11,Fannounced last week that energy bills
OL,12,Fwill fall by #117 for millions of
OL,13,FBritish households from April.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
